The <strong><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></strong> event object is available inside handler functions for the <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event">pageshow</a></code> and <code><a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pagehide_event">pagehide</a></code> events, fired when a document is being loaded or unloaded.